Question: Write a summary (plot synopsis) of your favorite movie.
Answer:
In To Kill A Mockingbird, Atticus Finch teaches his two young children about many injustices and discriminatory tendencies of the south.  Later in the story, as the children become more self aware, Atticus, an attorney, must represent a black man accusedof raping a white lady.  It is an incredible tale of acceptance and growth through a tragic but beautiful lense.